        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. Maximum likelihood tree for the concatenated matrix of all gene fragments (main figure) and for the concatenated matrix of all genes except COI (inset; this shows only part of the tree). Branch length is shown proportional to relative divergence, as estimated by IQ-TREE; scale bar indicates 0.01 units. Outgroups (Bembidarenas, Argentinatochoides, and Andinodontis; Table 1) not depicted." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/555127" .

